---
title: Chorizo and Orzo Stew with Feta and Tortilla Crumble
description: Chorizo sausage adds bold flavour to this hearty stew.  It joins sweet peppers and fresh spinach in an aromatic tomato broth, before being topped with a spiced tortilla chip crumble and feta cheese.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-au-chorizo-et-a-lorzo-b73c08c0.jpg
